[/size]
[color=#9BBB59]Thanks to nsk13 for the Awesome Temptra Thief Armor find
it here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59451/?

Because there is so many variants you won't need the original,
just install this and find the book in the thieves guild
headquarters for crafting. This armor set contains the 2k textures.
Get the hi-res 4k textures from the original mod page if you like,
install them last.

This set requires HDT High Heel System and the TBBP variant
requires either HDTPE or TBBP enabled animations and XPMSE 2.14
skeleton. You'll also want Dream Girl of course.

Enjoy![/color]
